    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Unit of storage measurement, specifically a collection of 8 bits, in digital technology, or computers. It represents a value, or code, for an individual character or typographic symbol.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
